 loading="lazy" title="利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 于格拉斯顿伯里和纳内沃斯 (Glastonbury &amp; Knebworth) 的石玫瑰 (The Stone Roses) 演出第一" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/j27A15yBBE8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他消息中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/support-acts-revealed-liam-gallagher-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-uk-ireland-tour-3557169">加拉格尔即将在英国和爱尔兰举办的“Definitely Maybe Tour”巡演的支持活动最近得到了证实</a>。</p><p>音乐行业高管、唱片公司所有者兼 Oasis 前经理 Alan McGee<a href="https://www.instagram.com/alanmcgee93/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在 Instagram 上</a>宣布，明年 6 月英国和爱尔兰演出的支持将来自独立乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cast">Cast</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-view">The View</a> 。</p><p>在宣布支持活动之前，有消息称加拉格尔<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-adds-belfast-date-with-kasabian-to-definitely-maybe-2024-tour-show-buy-tickets-3552038">最近在他 8 月 16 日举行的“Definitely Maybe”巡演中添加了与 Kasabian 一起在贝尔法斯特演出</a>。</p><p>据透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-to-play-oasis-definitely-maybe-in-full-at-reading-leeds-2024-3548140">加拉格尔将于明年夏天在雷丁和利兹举办他的“Definitely Maybe”演出</a>。他将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/BLINK-182">Blink-182</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/FRED-AGAIN">Fred Again..</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gerry-cinnamon">Gerry Cinnamon</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/catfish-and-the-bottlemen">Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen</a>一起成为 2024 年音乐节的主角。</p><p>此外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/trnsmt-2024-liam-gallagher-gerry-cinmamon-calvin-harris-lead-line-up-3545593">加拉格尔计划在明年格拉斯哥的 TRNSMT 音乐节上占据榜首</a>，此前他声称他的兄弟和前乐队成员<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-says-noel-gallagher-turned-down-definitely-maybe-tour-3516455">诺埃尔曾被邀请参加这次特别巡演，但他“拒绝了”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="http